title: 'Likely caused by strangulation': Doctor who observed Jeffrey Epstein autopsy makes shock claim about his death
summary_full: Newly released Justice Department files reignite questions surrounding Jeffrey Epstein's death in a New York jail cell.  Despite being on suicide watch and under heightened surveillance, significant lapses in protocol occurred, including missed inmate counts and unreplaced cellmates.  The circumstances of his death remain a subject of scrutiny.
